config MTK_MLOG
	bool "Support memory log"
	default y
	help
          Periodic memory log module.

		  Mlog will tracking memory usage include meminfo, buddy system,
		  hardware memory and process memory and oom_score_adj.
		  Enable this may casue a little memory buffer overhead but keep
		  tracking previous memory status. For dump memory usage,
		  please cat /d/mlog for persistent memory dump.
